{"tid":1556463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府教我如何正確使用扶手電梯","createTime":"2019-09-09T17:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T18:16:29.000Z","uid":292964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1e66d687c0cfa6886685b7cc4ae883c334b43ddb","tid":1556463,"uid":292964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:36:49.000Z","msg":"P牌第一次開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家比少少時間睇睇<br />\n我有兩個朋友最近問我點樣搭扶手電梯<br />\n我話 梗係要緊握扶手啦 好危險架<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.emsd.gov.hk/filemanager/tc/content_826/emsd_Mcdull_booklet-final.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.emsd.gov.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Ftc%2Fcontent_826%2Femsd_Mcdull_booklet-final.pdf&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNq9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=c1fad02e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.emsd.gov.hk/filemanager/tc/content_826/emsd_Mcdull_booklet-final.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OjRL9r1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOjRL9r1.png&h=04641d40&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z186TTH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ186TTH.png&h=b033b7df&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BQiiK0o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBQiiK0o.png&h=832a11d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢係扶手電梯比人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以失平衡想捉緊扶手<br />\n等到企穩啦 先慢慢放鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家千其唔好做標題黨啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9250f61bceabf38aed53ea594fa230cc645109","tid":1556463,"uid":292964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:37:16.000Z","msg":"哎呀唔小心開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959a6fbf6160